Good evening all. Just wanted to do a quick update from today since there was a lot going on. Got a beautiful sunrise this morning and printed some artwork and then going to do a installation of two pretty cool pieces. Just wanted to say happy holidays to all our family, friends and followers. Thanks so much for your love and support this year. As we are closing down to the end of the year I’m just so thankful. Please leave a comment of your thoughts and how your holidays are going and what you’re thankful for. Thanks again and have a great evening.

#Sunrise #WaterPhotography #Photography #Art #WaveArt #OceanFineArt #ArtOnMetal #Beach #Waves #Water #SanClemente #LagunaBeach #HumpbackWhales #larrybeard

Happy New Year’s all. I just wanted to bring you the sunset on the first day of 2023. But the main thing is I wanted to wish you guys all a happy new year. I hope 22 was good for you. And for all of us I wish 23 is going to be even better. Happy new year and please leave a comment. I would love to hear from you on the first day of this new year. Peace and love.

Good morning all. I got out early this morning and was fortunate enough to witness this mom feeding her baby. Priceless are not priceless? Give me your thoughts. LOL Have a great day!

Good Sunday Morning. 
I got up early this morning to see the sunrise and it did not disappoint. It looks like it was going to be too cloudy but God had something else in store. Have a great day all.

Wow I cannot believe how much snow is up here. We are along the 395 in lone Pine. I have never seen this much snow up here. Please leave me a comment if you have seen the snow like this or haven’t. I really encourage anyone who wants to get out this is the time.

#Snow #Snowstorms #395 #Mammoth #Mountains 
#Winter

I just wanted to get on here and share some of this beauty. We came out to Yosemite To try to capture some of this historic weather that we’re getting. And I am telling you it is absolutely gorgeous up here. Hope you’re having a blessed weekend. Give me a comment if you have any thoughts. Love you all.

#EpicSnow #Yosemite 
#YosemiteFalls #Mountains #Beauty #Sunrise #Photography #EpicSnow #LarryBeard #Sony #Landscape #LandscapePhotography #ArtOnMetal #FineArt #fineartphotography

Wow. I can’t believe us know has come. We are here up in Yosemite and have extended our trip considering this snowstorm was supposed to come in. It was raining only an hour ago. Was hoping it would turn into snow like they were saying it would. And it is here. Dumping right now. I can’t wait for the Beautiful photos that I might get. As you see this video please leave me a comment with your thoughts.

Good Saturday morning. We have a install today we are doing. A friend/client that has a dental office is getting four new pieces. Three of them have never been printed before. Super excited. My friend Nelson gets the fact that he can alter his clients experience by having amazing art on the walls. so check out this video and tell me what you think of these new pieces. I always love to hear your comments. Have a great Saturday. Mahalos

Great News!
The Rhythm & Resin Festival is this  Saturday down on Los Molinos in San Clemente. A great event celebrating surfing, shaping, music, art, the WSL Final and more. Come and join me at on of the more important events held here in San Clemente. Starting the Shaper Hall Of Fame for one. I will be releasing our “Forever John John” ( not the one in this post). Lol. Checkout the flyer in this post and we will be giving away a free print to anyone who mentions this post.

This photo of @john_john_florence is one of my favorite surfing images. Please leave a comment what are your thoughts of this photo. Thanks @john_john_florence
